            'Focus on facts, not interpretations',
            'Be specific about when and where',
            'Avoid adding your thoughts or feelings here',
            'Think of this as what a camera would capture'
          ]
        },
        {
          letter: 'B',
          title: 'Beliefs & Thoughts',
